      "en": "Which one is a one-to-one function?",
      "bn": "কোনটি এক-এক ফাংশন?",
      "opts": [
        "\\(f(x) = x^2\\)",
        "\\(f(x) = |x|\\)",
        "\\(f(x) = 2x + 1\\)",
        "\\(f(x) = \\sin x\\)"
      ],
      "ans": 2,
      "sol": [
        {
          "t": "A linear function \\(f(x) = 2x+1\\) is strictly increasing, hence one-to-one."
        },
