          "m": 4,
          "q": "Find \\(a^2 + b^2\\) and \\(a^2 - b^2\\). \\(a^2 + b^2\\) ও \\(a^2 - b^2\\) নির্ণয় করো।",
          "sol": [
            {
              "m": "a^2 = 3 + 2\\sqrt{6} + 2 = 5 + 2\\sqrt{6}"
            },
            {
              "m": "b^2 = 3 - 2\\sqrt{6} + 2 = 5 - 2\\sqrt{6}"
            },
            {
              "m": "a^2 + b^2 = \\boxed{10}"
            },
            {
              "m": "a^2 - b^2 = 4\\sqrt{6} = \\boxed{4\\sqrt{6}}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "l": "গ",
          "m": 4,
          "q": "Show that \\(\\frac{a}{b} + \\frac{b}{a} = 10\\). দেখাও যে \\(\\frac{a}{b} + \\frac{b}{a} = 10\\)।",
